AQAAMAAJ|title=Emergence of Islam in Kerala in 20th century|last=Kurup|first=K. K. N.|last2=Ismail|first2=E.|last3=India)|first3=Maulana Abul Kalam Azad Institute of Asian Studies (Calcutta|date=2008|publisher=Standard Publishers (India)|isbn=|location=|pages=379|language=en}}</ref> monthly, first in [[Arabi Malayalam|Arabic Malayalam]] and then in [[Malayalam]] in 1954.\n\n==See also==\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://samastha.info/}}\n\n{{Islam in Kerala}}\n\n[[Category:Sunni Islam in India]]\n[[Category:Islam in Kerala]]\n[[Category:Defunct organisations based in India]]\n[[Category:Samastha]]\n", "name_user": "49.15.81.74", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samastha"}
